# @sfcr/core

- Solver, parser, graph, engine, and fixtures live here.
- No React, DOM, workers, or browser APIs.
- Export through `src/index.ts`; consumers use `@sfcr/core`.
- When changing solver behavior, consider parity against `references/java/` or `references/r-sfcr/`.
- Tests: `packages/core/test/` (e.g. `core.test.ts`). Run `pnpm --filter @sfcr/core test`.
- Use `import type` for type-only imports (`verbatimModuleSyntax: true`).
